Three scripts to help verify nagios / icinga configuration.

my-monitor-testconf: Check syntax of nagios / icinga configuration in current
directory in a "nagios" and "icinga" schroot.

my-monitor-copy-and-check: Used by my-monitor-testconf.  Copies configuration
to a temporary directory, rewrites paths, and checks syntax.

my-monitor-update-schroots: Script to prepare schroots used for testing.
